WEBVTT



00:00:12.992 --> 00:00:21.024
The recent so-called 12-day war refers to a conflict between Israel and Iran that began June 13, 2025.

00:00:21.088 --> 00:00:28.544
Longstanding tensions, particularly over Iran's nuclear program and regional influence, had escalated to the point that Israel launched

00:00:28.320 --> 00:00:38.368
Operation Rising Lion, a surprise attack targeting Iran's nuclear facilities, ballistic missile infrastructure, and key military and scientific

00:00:37.888 --> 00:00:39.456
Scientific personnel.

00:00:39.584 --> 00:00:42.688
The operation was framed as a preemptive strike

00:00:42.496 --> 00:00:45.920
to prevent Iran from developing nuclear weapons.

00:00:45.792 --> 00:00:49.536
Iran responded with missile and drone attacks on Israel.

00:00:49.248 --> 00:00:52.384
Marking the start of the 12-day conflict.

00:00:52.576 --> 00:00:58.496
The shortness of the war was reminiscent of the Six-Day War of June, nineteen, sixty seven.

00:00:58.592 --> 00:01:01.280
when the Jews regained all of Jerusalem.

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:04.832
Long drawn-out conflicts seem to be the norm.

00:01:04.768 --> 00:01:08.544
like the ongoing conflict between Russia and Ukraine.

00:01:08.736 --> 00:01:11.968
The Crusades lasted nearly 300 years.

00:01:11.712 --> 00:01:17.312
In the so-called 100-year war was waged between England and France.

00:01:17.472 --> 00:01:23.136
No stranger to this phenomenon, the Arab-Israeli conflict has dragged on for many decades.

00:01:23.488 --> 00:01:29.952
However, God has granted Israel these swift victories, the Six-Day War of June 1967,

00:01:29.792 --> 00:01:36.960
and now the remarkable 12-day war between Israel and Iran in June 2025.

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:44.704
The war ended soon after America's brave decision to utterly destroy Iran's nuclear program with direct strikes.

00:01:44.672 --> 00:01:50.400
By 14 giant bunker busting bombs on three main Iranian facilities.

00:01:50.592 --> 00:01:54.240
Neighborhoods will assassinate at all of the Ron's nuclear scientists.

00:01:53.984 --> 00:01:57.152
in at least 30 of Iran's top generals.

00:01:57.280 --> 00:02:02.880
Israel's success in this war will be studied in more colleges worldwide for decades to come.

00:02:03.328 --> 00:02:07.424
According to a report by Pastor David Decker in Jerusalem,

00:02:07.392 --> 00:02:11.008
The damage to Israel over these 12 days was severe.

00:02:10.880 --> 00:02:15.456
Including 28 dead and over 3,000 hospitalized.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:17.504
23 seriously wounded.

00:02:17.792 --> 00:02:23.520
550 ballistic missiles were aimed at Israel, of which 36 made impact.

00:02:23.456 --> 00:02:26.400
all over central and northern Israel.

00:02:26.336 --> 00:02:29.280
but especially in the greater Tel Aviv area.

00:02:29.184 --> 00:02:34.592
where over a million Israelis barely left their shelters for 12 days and nights.

00:02:34.912 --> 00:02:38.528
About 15,000 Israelis were rendered homeless.

00:02:38.464 --> 00:02:42.304
Filling Israeli hotels with refugees rather than tourists.

00:02:42.336 --> 00:02:47.424
The total damage to the Israeli economy was close to $10 billion.

00:02:47.552 --> 00:02:55.232
Israel intercepted over 90% of missiles and knocked all of their thousand drones out of the sky, except for just two.

00:02:56.384 --> 00:02:58.912
Christian Zionist Mike Huckabee

00:02:58.816 --> 00:03:04.160
